## Packages Used

### Backend (`backend/package.json`)

| Package             | Purpose                                    |
|---------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| express             | HTTP server framework                      |
| @prisma/client      | Database ORM (SQLite)                      |
| prisma              | Schema management and migrations           |
| bcrypt              | Password hashing                           |
| jsonwebtoken        | JWT token creation and verification        |
| express-jwt         | JWT middleware for route protection         |
| cors                | Cross-origin request handling              |
| helmet              | Security response headers                  |
| express-rate-limit  | Rate limiting middleware                   |
| zod                 | Schema-based input validation              |
| multer              | File upload handling (avatars, resumes)     |
| socket.io           | Real-time WebSocket communication          |
| dotenv              | Environment variable loading               |
| uuid                | Unique ID generation                       |
| sqlite3             | SQLite database driver                     |

NOTE: Backend packages were added AFTER A2 submission and were not present in A2
These were added for additional security as I want to present this project in my portfolio
and adding these would improve that

